{"tid":1689822,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈 - 手作人好需要你","createTime":"2019-11-03T04:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T19:19:11.000Z","uid":179231,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4378ef655ed7e9fd67b371e5892f29144e4c5559","tid":1689822,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"我只係一個全職OL，只敢行向中間，驚死無用(但絕對唔會一放TG就奔跑，求下大家唔好再奔跑好嘛？)<br />\n<br />\n我一直都整開手作仔，去香港手作展都見到好多香港人係做手作搵食，但香港手作永遠都好似只可以係興趣咁，點解唔可以係搵食? 明明大家見到香港文宣都做得好靚&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n成立黃色經濟圈係我近排不同諗有咩可以做到，錢我唔多亦唔係做開生意。但每個月再慳D, 幾千我都可以afford 到，我相信有心就可以，一步一步黎。<br />\n<br />\n所以我開咗個page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HandcraftStation-108398293936563/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHandcraftStation-108398293936563%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=c77b768b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HandcraftStation-108398293936563/</a><br />\n<br />\n第一步: 我需要得到你哋嘅like，請like個page<br />\n第二步: 如果你係手作人又同意我個諗法，可以請你inbox我嘛？未需要即刻決定寄賣，但我想得到你哋嘅意見<br />\n第三步: 當有手作人回覆我之後，我會自己出錢整個online shop，大家可以上網買。而手作人嘅成品係會將成品寄存向一個點集合寄出(我計過我可以負擔到一個月3000蚊租去做呢樣嘢)<br />\n<br />\n我未諗到點收手作人錢，抽成?義賣?大家歡迎比意見&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\nDefaults唔使講，50%盈利會捐到星火，50%會去支持黃色經濟圈(可能全買光時禮品卡之後捐比有需要人士)<br />\n<br />\n首先，請大家一點支持，Like個Page同<br />\nshare比你識嘅手作人知🙏"},{"pid":"0593505a6b472441b074eb8976f02428e0c626b8","tid":1689822,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:22:32.000Z","msg":"Push support"},{"pid":"3cbe4c8dd1e24613020cbaabd7cc29c50fad9761","tid":1689822,"uid":311337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"40e26bd1a9b5fe2859f5e7aa4ffcb7194f3c4697","tid":1689822,"uid":1212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"Support"},{"pid":"6fb28d7b20093e025fa34634cec697ef9e8422f4","tid":1689822,"uid":263949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"任何新諗法都必須推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都要諗下點令多啲人加入 畢竟如果佢地本身都有run開ig shop儲到班客仔 而加入咗又要抽太多捐 我諗佢地未必肯join<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有冇理解錯 請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c237f45cd075cd7234405efe2af0f1062b3df1b2","tid":1689822,"uid":181393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8241bd8b02b2b8dfdb087aaf8cd01f6ccdbcb9c1","tid":1689822,"uid":181393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"Push again"},{"pid":"312df3bae1cbfd76efcf09647bcf086c0f5cfcb7","tid":1689822,"uid":281181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:18:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dea74316755b3021a95b2721f568edfe6ba2ca56","tid":1689822,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb28d7b20093e025fa34634cec697ef9e8422f4","tid":1689822,"uid":263949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"任何新諗法都必須推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都要諗下點令多啲人加入 畢竟如果佢地本身都有run開ig shop儲到班客仔 而加入咗又要抽太多捐 我諗佢地未必肯join<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有冇理解錯 請指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:25:02.000Z","msg":"我唔諗住抽太多，其實應該講都唔知要抽幾多，學生嘅唔抽? 但我想可以請到一個手足幫手影相，上架，答客人問題，推廣，寄貨。咁又可以令到手作人更加專心做創作"},{"pid":"c53a7aeb50c755432835f7fa5414274b81efc852","tid":1689822,"uid":179231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"自己又再推一下先"},{"pid":"f84c2e1b485711288b6386b8526857ae1beed537","tid":1689822,"uid":11485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"寫字義賣OK?"},{"pid":"fc73cf5b9bb307a446242aa468f6b2665c16f696","tid"